OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dull and damp start to the
OL,6,Fday. However, it should become drier
OL,7,Fand brighter through the morning with
OL,8,Fa few sunny spells developing for the
OL,9,Fafternoon, although parts of Devon and
OL,10,FCornwall could remain cloudy. Warm in
OL,11,Fthe sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,14,Fthis evening across eastern counties,
OL,15,Fhowever thicker cloud already across
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall will become more
OL,17,Fwidespread overnight, with some patchy
OL,18,Fdrizzle developing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
