OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith further outbreaks of mostly light
OL,7,Fdrizzle, mainly across the hills and
OL,8,Fmoors. A more organised band of rain
OL,9,Farriving from the northwest in the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FCloud
OL,13,Fclearing early on Thursday, then fine
OL,14,Fwith some sunshine. Turning unsettled
OL,15,Fover the Easter weekend with showers
OL,16,For longer spells of rain. Some strong
OL,17,Fand gusty winds too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
